1. Install the following software

     GLPK library   
          http://www.gnu.org/software/glpk/

     ocaml-glpk
          http://ocaml-glpk.sourceforge.net/

2. Run "make spica" in the source directory.
   
   If the make is successful, 
   spica.exe (or spica in Linux) will be created.

  
     




